  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with a diagnosis of Chronic renal disease (end stage) in hemodialysis for at
             least 3 months

          -  Diagnosis of Major depression disorder (4 or more clinical criteria in MINI and a BDI
             score of 10 or more)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients in process of renal transplant with (living donor)

          -  Psychiatric comorbidity

          -  Cognitive impairment or mental retardation

          -  Current substance abuse

          -  Heart failure, angina pectoris, arrhythmias
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
